All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class GridClosureException
extends GridRuntimeException

This exception provides closures with facility to throw exceptions. Closures can't throw checked exception and this class provides a standard idiom on how to wrap and pass an exception up the call chain. It is also frequently used with GridEither to return either wrapping exception or value from the closure.
